data.description: Beautifully remodeled Farmhouse Style Home, sits on 1.39 acres in Keithville, outside the city limits. You will enjoy sipping your morning or afternoon coffee on this large front porch. Three large bedrooms and two full baths with the primary suite having a huge walk-in closet, stand alone bathtub and oversized walk in shower, a breakfast bar and spacious living room with vaulted ceilings with cedar beams and a cozy fireplace. SHIPLAP GALORE! So beautiful. Everything is brand new. Must see to appreciate.
